subprocess, stdout envelope, and persisted artifact.\\\\n- Verified `AC-4.2 / TC-4.2a` via [provider-adapter.test.ts](/Users/leemoore/code/liminal-spec/processes/impl-cli/tests/provider-adapter.test.ts:372) and [provider-adapter.test.ts](/Users/leemoore/code/liminal-spec/processes/impl-cli/tests/provider-adapter.test.ts:446); these hit the real adapter code against PATH fixture binaries and assert explicit `codex exec resume --json <session-id>` / `claude --resume <session-id>` behavior with no latest-session fallback.\\\\n- Verified `AC-4.2 / TC-4.2b` via [story-implement-command.test.ts](/Users/leemoore/code/liminal-spec/processes/impl-cli/tests/story-implement-command.test.ts:218); the CLI returns provider, sessionId, and continuation handle needed by `story-continue`.\\\\n- Verified `AC-4.3 / TC-4.3a` via [story-implement-command.test.ts](/Users/leemoore/code/liminal-spec/processes/impl-cli/tests/story-implement-command.test.ts:344), with stop-branch coverage in [story-implement-command.test.ts](/Users/leemoore/code/liminal-spec/processes/impl-cli/tests/story-implement-command.test.ts:167) and [story-implement-command.test.ts](/Users/leemoore/code/liminal-spec/processes/impl-cli/tests/story-implement-command.test.ts:619); this covers full-pass, blocked-stop, and human-ruling-stop paths through the public CLI.\\\\n- Verified `AC-4.3 / TC-4.3b` via runtime coverage in [story-implement-command.test.ts](/Users/leemoore/code/liminal-spec/processes/impl-cli/tests/story-implement-command.test.ts:441); it inspects the actual logged provider prompts for pass 1/2/3. [prompt-assembly.test.ts](/Users/leemoore/code/liminal-spec/processes/impl-cli/tests/prompt-assembly.test.ts:356) adds unit coverage.\\\\n- Verified `AC-4.4 / TC-4.4a` via [story-implement-command.test.ts](/Users/leemoore/code/liminal-spec/processes/impl-cli/tests/story-implement-command.test.ts:503); same-session self-review returns recorded `findingsFixed` without a fresh session.\\\\n- Verified `AC-4.4 / TC